<HL>
   Guitar-Pickers Are Making a Market
   ---
   Rock of Ages Spurs
   Old-Model Prices
   ----
   By Robert Tomsho
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/08/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C1
</SO>
<MS>
